- Natural Herbal Alternative to Taking HRT", "cat": "capsules", "price": 19.94, "was": 20.99, "img": "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/168448037920.webp", "rev": 5, "out": false, "benefit": "Relief from Major Symptoms of Menopause| One a Day| 2 Months Supply", "gallery": ["https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/168448037920.webp", "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/1684480379721.webp", "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/1684480379632.webp", "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/1684480379533.webp", "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/1684480379744.webp", "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/16844803791005.webp"], "packs": [["Single Product", 19.94], ["Pack of 2 Bottles", 18.89], ["Pack of 3 Bottles", 17.85], ["Pack of 4 Bottles", 16.79]], "stock": 183, "id": 24, "goals": ["menopause"], "size": "60 Vegan Capsules", "desc": "<p>Naturaljuices Natural Alternative to HRT contains highest-quality concentrated extracts of 7 key menopause herbs. These herbal extracts contain an abundance of naturally occurring phytochemicals that help your body cope with the complex hormonal changes encountered during menopause \u2014 it is the combination of superior standardised extracts in precisely balanced quantities that makes it so effective. Scientifically developed and validated through human clinical trials.</p><p>Within 30 days many women notice a significant reduction in menopause symptoms such as hot flushes, night sweats, mood swings, irritability, headaches, sleep disturbances and tiredness. Each tub contains 60 high-potency one-a-day vegan capsules \u2014 a full 2 months' supply.</p>", "ing": "<p>Per capsule: Soy Isoflavones 40% \u2014 150mg \u00b7 Hops \u2014 150.3mg \u00b7 Sage Officinalis Extract 5:1 \u2014 30mg (equivalent to 150mg of Sage) \u00b7 Red Clover Extract 38:1 (equivalent to 1,140mg of Red Clover) \u00b7 Dong Quai 6:1 Extract \u2014 10mg (equivalent to 60mg of Dong Quai) \u00b7 Vitamin E Acetate 50%.</p><p>Vegan-friendly capsules. Made in the UK.</p>", "dir": "<p>Take one capsule per day with water when eating a meal. Not suitable if pregnant or breast-feeding. Keep out of reach of children. Food supplements are not a substitute for a varied diet \u2014 consult your GP before use if you are on medication or have a medical condition.</p>"}, {"name": "Coyne Healthcare Biomax Microactive CoQ10 Supplement", "cat": "capsules", "price": 25.64, "was": 26.99, "img": "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/162978309261Y-+seFlCL._AC_SL1000_.jpg", "rev": 0, "out": false, "benefit": "Clinically Proven 24hr Microactive Coenzyme", "gallery": ["https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/162978309261Y-+seFlCL._AC_SL1000_.jpg"], "packs": [], "stock": null, "id": 25, "goals": ["energy"], "size": "30 Vegetable Capsules"}, {"name": "Coyne Healthcare Bio Curcumin Supplement with Bcm95", "cat": "capsules", "price": 40.84, "was": 42.99, "img": "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/71tTElsgdNL._AC_SL1000_.jpg", "rev": 0, "out": false, "benefit": "Delivers 7 X More Free Curcumin", "gallery": ["https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/71tTElsgdNL._AC_SL1000_.jpg"], "packs": [], "stock": null, "id": 26, "goals": [], "size": "60 Vegetable Capsules"}, {"name": "Coyne Healthcare Liposomal Vitamin C", "cat": "capsules", "price": 37.99, "was": 39.99, "img": "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/1630045861Vitamin-C-Supplement-Biomax-60s-Group-Image-min.jpg", "rev": 0, "out": false, "benefit": "Deliver Vitamin C into Bloodstream", "gallery": ["https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/1630045861Vitamin-C-Supplement-Biomax-60s-Group-Image-min.jpg"], "packs": [], "stock": null, "id": 27, "goals": ["immunity"], "size": "60 Capsules"}, {"name": "Coyne Healthcare Biomax Activated VIT B Complex Liposomal", "cat": "capsules", "price": 19.42, "was": 20.44, "img": "https://www.naturaljuices.co.uk/images/products/162979048341km7K